<tr>
    <td align="center" valign="top" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px;">
        <table width="700" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="container"
               style="border:0px solid #d7d7d7;margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 0px; border-radius: 2px;">
            <tr style="width: 100%; vertical-align: top">
                <td align="left" style="vertical-align: top; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-right: 20px;" width="60" height="60">
                    <div style="position: relative; left: -9px; font-size: 24px;">
                        <img src="{{paralectUrl}}/common/logo/report-blue-60x60.png?1" align="middle" height="60" width="60" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 100%; padding-left: 0px;padding-top: 10px; color: #2c2c2c;">
                <span style="position: relative; top: 10px; left: 0px;">
                  <span style="font-size: 32px; color: #484848; text-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.95);">Weekly Report</span><br>
                  <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #777777;">{{range}}</span>
                </span>

                </td>
                <td valign="middle" align="right">
                    <a href="https://www.paralect.com" style="margin-bottom: 0px;">
                        <img alt="Paralect" height="47" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -8px; margin-right: -9px; height: 47px; border: 0; border-radius:2px; background-color: rgba(50,174,241,0.9);" src="{{logoUrl}}"/>
                    </a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td align="center" valign="top">
        <table width="700" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="container"
               style="border:1px solid #d7dfe6; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; background:white; border-radius: 2px;">
            <tr>
                <td style="padding: 30px 40px 35px 50px;">
                    <div>
                        <p>Hi {{clientFirstName}},</p>
                    </div>
                    <p>I prepared weekly time report for the last week ({{range}}). You can find
                        report in attachment.</p>

                    <p>Feel free to let me know if you found some mistakes. They will be corrected immediately!</p>

                    <p>You can always refer to this <a href="{{urlToDashboard}}">simple
                        dashboard</a> for all your invoices and recent payments.</p>

                    <p>Thank you for working with us!</p>

                    <p>Best regards,<br>Artem Kozlovsky<br>CFO, Paralect</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </td>
</tr>
